      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"TreasureDenoising-Denoising\">Denoising</h3><p>I used the RenderMan machine learning denoiser to great extent. It helped me a lot when I needed a quick turn-around for a test and was crucial to cut down on final render times, so that the image doesn't have to reach full convergence before the denoiser can clean things up.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon-coins-denoise-before.jpg\" width=\"292\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=292&amp;height=292\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"292\" data-width=\"292\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657555533\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon-coins-denoise-before.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657621139\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"264181ac-412c-47e8-9f1d-7b547ca8a8d1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=292&amp;height=292 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=292&amp;height=292 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon-coins-denoise-after.jpg\" width=\"292\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=292&amp;height=292\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"292\" data-width=\"292\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657555540\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon-coins-denoise-after.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657621139\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"2b04f9ce-ffd9-49ac-8f2a-7ab9e698b691\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=292&amp;height=292 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/dragon-coins-denoise-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=292&amp;height=292 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Inside the Render Elements Node, there are a variety of AOVs and LPEs which are ingested into the rendered EXR file. This gives the Denoise application the necessary data to execute.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"DENOISE_RENDER_SETUP.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/DENOISE_RENDER_SETUP.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756718&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=413\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657621139/DENOISE_RENDER_SETUP.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756718&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"926\" data-width=\"1700\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657555546\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DENOISE_RENDER_SETUP.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657621139\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"4c59c97a-503b-4929-a2f3-91cc7fdb73ea\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/DENOISE_RENDER_SETUP.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756718&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=826 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621139/DENOISE_RENDER_SETUP.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590756718&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=413 1x\"></span><hr/></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
